-teaser__content"><div class="o-teaser__meta"><span class="o-teaser__tag-prefix">READ MORE</span><a class="o-teaser__tag" data-trackable="teaser-tag" href="/content/8fe4af94-ab20-44f3-92c6-768c564b5cdb" aria-label="Category: Risk Management: Financial Institutions">Risk Management: Financial Institutions</a></div><div class="o-teaser__heading"><a href="https://www.ft.com/content/9a810c10-c887-40e5-a8c7-02aa0e111c93" data-trackable="heading-link" class="js-teaser-heading-link">Banks face new risks as US tightens sanctions on Russia</a></div></div><div class="o-teaser__image-container js-teaser-image-container"><a href="https://www.ft.com/content/9a810c10-c887-40e5-a8c7-02aa0e111c93" data-trackable="image-link" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true"><div class="o-teaser__image-placeholder" style="aspect-ratio:2292/1289"><img class="o-teaser__image" src="https://www.ft.com/__origami/service/image/v2/images/raw/https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2F__origami%2Fservice%2Fimage%2Fv2%2Fimages%2Fraw%2Fhttps%253A%252F%252Fd1e00ek4ebabms.cloudfront.net%252Fproduction%252F30013a80-e6b9-4493-95dd-7862e0446d3b.jpg%3Fsource%3Dnext-article%26fit%3Dscale-down%26quality%3Dhighest%26width%3D700%26dpr%3D1?source=next&amp;fit=scale-down&amp;dpr=2&amp;width=340" alt="A man giving a speech at a lectern with two microphones, in a room decorated with American flags, a large painting of a man riding a horse in a landscape, and plants in the background"/></div></a></div></div></div></div><div class="package__content-menu" data-trackable="menu-contents"><ul class="package__reset-ul"><li class="package__content-border"><a href="/content/c6e03d45-e29a-4c58-b23c-4ffaaf7ba0f2" class="package__content-item package__content-item--current-page" data-trackable="menu-item"><div class="package__content-item-headline"><div class="package__text--strong">Currently reading:</div><span class="package__title">Bond market liquidity squeeze keeps regulators alert to risks</span></div></a></li><li class="package__content-border